>>7f4463e8-7c82-45e6-9eeb-b8af67b85963
Clicking on [Seed] is very misleading, because often people are still seeding, but the site makes an error and tells you there's no one seeding. Click on the thumbnail and most images will load. I'm seeding all the images here, except for the broken TOR image and 3 other ones. The vast majority after clicking on [Seed] told me there were 0 seeds, but that was obviously wrong.

So basically ignore [Seed] and click to open the images instead to ensure you seed everything you want to seed.
